<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/733916-i-think-caste-of-all-kinds-should-be">I think caste of all kinds should be abolished. But why target Hinduism. Target the people who misinterpreted it and made the caste system?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_733916'><a id="like_count_community_question_733916" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/733916?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8521879-annihilation-of-caste">like</a></span>

</li>
