<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/13424240-pavan-dharanipragada"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1377988340i/13424240._UY100_CR24,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/13424240-pavan-dharanipragada">Pavan Dharanipragada</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Caste system is codified in all Vedas starting from the earliest Veda, the Rig Veda. So the claim that Hinduism has nothing to do with caste is plain <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Caste system is codified in all Vedas starting from the earliest Veda, the Rig Veda. So the claim that Hinduism has nothing to do with caste is plain wrong. Please read Dr. Ambedkar's book for a more precise argument.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
